The '''Corellian corpse-grub''' was a foul smelling worm that originated from [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] and fed on corpses. While devouring and rapidly skeletonizing its victims, it excreted a noxious effluvia.<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

